HEALTHCARE AND LIFE SCIENCE INVESTING




 ABOUT US



Opus Point…investing in Innovation



We are committed to identifying and investing in innovations in life science and healthcare that will change the way diseases are diagnosed, the way patients are cared for and the way healthcare and medicine are delivered to patients. We focus on investments in publicly-traded biotech and life sciences companies, through our hedge fund, Opus Point Healthcare Innovations Fund.  




