For Entrepreneurs




	Seed/Start-Up

	The principals are both experienced entrepreneurs who have founded, financed and operated multiple biotechnology companies over the last 20 years.  While we do not have an investment vehicle from which to invest in seed and start-up businesses, Opus Point would consider making small seed investments in highly selective circumstances from the partners’ capital.

	Entrepreneurs seeking to launch their biotechnology or life sciences business should contact our Senior Analyst, Lung Yam, M.D., Ph.D.  
	 

